    "originContent": "MINT (Multimeric INteraction Transformer) is a Protein Language Model (PLM) designed for **contextual and scalable** modeling of interacting protein sequences. Trained on a large, curated set of **96 million protein-protein interactions (PPIs)** from the STRING database, MINT outperforms existing PLMs across diverse tasks and protein types, including:",
