    "row": 145,
    "rowsha": "PHcq2hxm2WtbKw9/+8g856qTg+SSZ/ncVsk9ybhn+Ws=",
    "originContent": "Then, run the following commands to cluster the sequences using a 50% sequence similarity threshold using [mmseqs](https://github.com/soedinglab/MMseqs2).",
    "translatedContent": "Luego, ejecute los siguientes comandos para agrupar las secuencias utilizando un umbral de similitud de secuencia del 50 % usando [mmseqs](https://github.com/soedinglab/MMseqs2)."
  },
  {
    "row": 146,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 147,
    "rowsha": "8bkBhHOQsO1+N058HkZOwXtGpCfEh6WtbL0pBkBQg9U=",
